N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4009.7 - Mutilated tickets

State Regulations

Mutilated pari-mutuel tickets or those whose validity
is questioned shall be submitted to the New York State Department of Taxation
and Finance for inspection, and the ruling of said Department of Taxation and

Finance thereon shall be final and conclusive. Notes
